WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.040 --> 00:00:03.580
Do you know that Lin Bang is already ill

2
00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:07.340
Are you doing this now because you're afraid he'll die too soon?

3
00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:10.160
No matter what disease you have

4
00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:12.340
We will never let this house

5
00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:16.220
Otherwise, I will send it to the TV station. You can't do it.

6
00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:21.180
Then you will be accused of adultery for the rest of your life

7
00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:23.300
It's our family business

8
00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:24.960
It's not your turn to point fingers

9
00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:27.220
Get out of here! That's enough

10
00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:30.720
Tono

11
00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:32.160
Why are you here?

12
00:00:32.160 --> 00:00:34.880
If I don't come again, my uncle will be forced to die by you.

13
00:00:34.880 --> 00:00:35.900
Not your uncle

14
00:00:35.920 --> 00:00:37.000
If he wasn't my uncle

15
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:38.120
Then you are not my mother

16
00:00:38.120 --> 00:00:39.700
What the hell are you talking about?

17
00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:41.080
With you just for profit

18
00:00:41.080 --> 00:00:44.840
But Qianqian's mother and grandma and grandpa, I won't let you

19
00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:47.360
What's wrong with you kid?

20
00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:48.480
Are you talking nonsense?

21
00:00:48.480 --> 00:00:49.780
Ah Tongtong

22
00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:51.280
Do you know what you're saying?

23
00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:52.280
Of course I do.

24
00:00:52.280 --> 00:00:54.400
Don't you just want me to be like this?

25
00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:55.900
How dare you destroy your elders

26
00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:58.040
This is what I usually teach you

27
00:00:58.040 --> 00:00:59.620
Actions speak louder than words

28
00:00:59.800 --> 00:01:02.400
I have been told what you did.

29
00:01:02.400 --> 00:01:03.520
Can't be a good person

30
00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:05.120
Otherwise, you can only be bullied

31
00:01:05.120 --> 00:01:07.280
If you dare to talk nonsense in the future, believe it or not, I will kill you.

32
00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:09.180
Come on, fight

33
00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:10.620
You hit me today

34
00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:12.800
When you are old, I will beat you every day

35
00:01:12.800 --> 00:01:13.760
How did I beat you?

36
00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:14.980
You are such an unfilial daughter

37
00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:18.060
I told you, you taught me that.

38
00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:20.000
Since you treat money as dung

39
00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.620
Then I should be like you

40
00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:23.040
No matter if others live or die

41
00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:24.260
Just for yourself

